    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain access to all uncommon weapons with the Seillian trait. You have familiarity with weapons with the Seillian trait plus @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.MVAWttmT0QDa7LsV]{Longbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.dUC8Fsa6FZtVikS3]{Composite Longbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.grmaV4GdoGD7sKbn]{Scimitars}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.hIgqLgH3YcLZBeoT]{Shortbows}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.e4NwsnPnpQKbDZ9F]{Composite Shortbows}—for the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.</p><p>At 5th level, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.</p>",
      "gm": ""
